{"tid":1269111,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔想再有第三個，請廣傳，感謝各位","createTime":"2019-06-30T12:58:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T14:43:05.000Z","uid":125349,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6d54aed0f8e65a8dcc48a0bdc234eed907d78512","tid":1269111,"uid":125349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T12:58:01.000Z","msg":"我哋，熱愛同一片土地。<br />\n<br />\n我哋，流緊同一種血。<br />\n<br />\n政府既謊言、極權、槍彈，正摧毀每個人的未來。<br />\n<br />\n呢片土地，危在旦夕。<br />\n<br />\n撤惡法、查黑警、釋放義士。每個街上既呼聲，為左一個共同既希望&mdash;&mdash;自由。<br />\n<br />\n因為愛，因為希望，而不再孤單、不再恐懼。<br />\n<br />\n勇者無懼，成就今日我哋強大既力量。<br />\n<br />\n從今日起，我哋將會主動迎戰，推翻高牆，從政府手中、重奪屬於每個人既自由與未來。<br />\n<br />\n革命之心，遍地開花。<br />\n<br />\n我哋，叫做「香港人」。"},{"pid":"c59515b36eaedb7eb46e179a21e99ab43354e5e2","tid":1269111,"uid":63461,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推<br />\n香港人加油"},{"pid":"2002b6e4001caee37493b45fcee2b3f8c30e0221","tid":1269111,"uid":125349,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:03:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"10e7cea7d2f22620f8f981630c0fc23e6e6bbb5c","tid":1269111,"uid":229351,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:06:40.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人一齊走落去"},{"pid":"8942f1ec6c4d40b58dbc39aa74c5a11cf3c893c5","tid":1269111,"uid":247501,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:23:53.000Z","msg":"心很痛"},{"pid":"ccb5220e0af0eb1d34f7b92a87f7744f769c4afb","tid":1269111,"uid":125349,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:05:45.000Z","msg":"唔想再多一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e6a5c4c66baa75e3a369a7d2805e69018483d1","tid":1269111,"uid":163900,"like":0,"dislike":1,"sc